  "detailed_description": "<h1>Join Our Discord!</h1><p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >FLY</h2>Fly, Build & Share! Take control of a paper plane and soar through a variety of levels that will challenge your skills and reflexes. The gameplay is easy to pick up, but difficult to master - so get ready to put your skills to the test!<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2106960/extras/1e04708daadfbeab1e34c3ea8d7ca316.poster.avif?t=1699949081\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2106960/extras/1e04708daadfbeab1e34c3ea8d7ca316.webm?t=1699949081\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2106960/extras/1e04708daadfbeab1e34c3ea8d7ca316.mp4?t=1699949081\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >BUILD</h2>But the fun doesn't stop there! With the included level editor, you can unleash your creativity by building your own levels and experimenting with a wide variety of tiles and objects to design the ultimate paper plane challenge. The sky is the limit!<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2106960/extras/5009327889ffe1c3843cf7ab2e5e37fe.poster.avif?t=1699949081\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2106960/extras/5009327889ffe1c3843cf7ab2e5e37fe.webm?t=1699949081\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2106960/extras/5009327889ffe1c3843cf7ab2e5e37fe.mp4?t=1699949081\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >SHARE</h2>And if that's not enough, you can also share your levels with the world! Challenge others to beat your creations or play community-made levels yourself. There's always something new to discover and conquer in this exciting and endlessly creative game!<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2106960/extras/f9eb68e78ffdf330201b2b4c290de1e5.poster.avif?t=1699949081\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2106960/extras/f9eb68e78ffdf330201b2b4c290de1e5.webm?t=1699949081\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2106960/extras/f9eb68e78ffdf330201b2b4c290de1e5.mp4?t=1699949081\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >FLY</h2>Fly, Build & Share! Take control of a paper plane and soar through a variety of levels that will challenge your skills and reflexes. The gameplay is easy to pick up, but difficult to master - so get ready to put your skills to the test!<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2106960/extras/1e04708daadfbeab1e34c3ea8d7ca316.poster.avif?t=1699949081\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2106960/extras/1e04708daadfbeab1e34c3ea8d7ca316.webm?t=1699949081\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2106960/extras/1e04708daadfbeab1e34c3ea8d7ca316.mp4?t=1699949081\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >BUILD</h2>But the fun doesn't stop there! With the included level editor, you can unleash your creativity by building your own levels and experimenting with a wide variety of tiles and objects to design the ultimate paper plane challenge. The sky is the limit!<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2106960/extras/5009327889ffe1c3843cf7ab2e5e37fe.poster.avif?t=1699949081\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2106960/extras/5009327889ffe1c3843cf7ab2e5e37fe.webm?t=1699949081\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2106960/extras/5009327889ffe1c3843cf7ab2e5e37fe.mp4?t=1699949081\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >SHARE</h2>And if that's not enough, you can also share your levels with the world! Challenge others to beat your creations or play community-made levels yourself. There's always something new to discover and conquer in this exciting and endlessly creative game!<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2106960/extras/f9eb68e78ffdf330201b2b4c290de1e5.poster.avif?t=1699949081\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2106960/extras/f9eb68e78ffdf330201b2b4c290de1e5.webm?t=1699949081\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2106960/extras/f9eb68e78ffdf330201b2b4c290de1e5.mp4?t=1699949081\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
